	Rosa Portillo&nbsp;- Case Manager Specialist
</p>
<p data-zesty-id="content:wysiwyg_basic:49:25">
	Pamela Streiter - Office Coordinator,<a href="mailto:pamela.streiter@uss.salvationarmy.org" target="">&nbsp;pamela.streiter@uss.salvationarmy.org</a>
</p>
<div class="my-2" data-zesty-id="design:design:whitespace-sm:50:10"></div>
